flowchart TD
  Topic[Active Topic]
  Topic -->|GetTopicContent| Sections["Topic Sections / Parent Content (heading + content)"]

  subgraph Generation[Topic-Based Content Generation]
    Qz[Generate Quiz]
    Fg[Generate Flashcards]
    QzPrompt[Build quiz prompt from sections]
    FgPrompt[Build flashcard prompt from sections]
    QzLLM[LLM generates JSON quiz]
    FgLLM[LLM generates JSON flashcards]
    QzSave[Persist 5 quiz questions]
    FgSave[Persist 8 flashcards]
  end

  Sections --> QzPrompt --> QzLLM --> QzSave
  Sections --> FgPrompt --> FgLLM --> FgSave

  subgraph Review[Study / Examiner Flow]
    QuizStart[User takes quiz question]
    QuizAnswer[Submit answer]
    Score[ScoreAnswer / normalize + compare]
    FlashcardShow[Show flashcard prompt]
    FlashcardGrade[User rating: again/hard/good/easy]
    FSRS[Update due date via FSRS scheduler]
  end

  QzSave --> QuizStart
  QuizStart --> QuizAnswer --> Score -->|store quiz score| Topic

  FgSave --> FlashcardShow --> FlashcardGrade --> FSRS -->|update card due_at| Topic

  style Generation fill:#f5f3ff,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:1px
  style Review fill:#ecfeff,stroke:#0e7490,stroke-width:1px
  style Topic fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,stroke-width:1px
  style Sections fill:#f0fdf4,stroke:#15803d,stroke-width:1px